.SS "List< \fBMarkupElement\fP > SlimeMarkUp\&.Core\&.MarkupParser\&.Parse (string text)"

.PP
Parses the specified markup text and returns a collection of markup elements representing its structure\&. YAML front matter and document properties blocks at the beginning of the input are automatically excluded from parsing\&. Lines not recognized by registered extensions are treated as paragraphs by default\&. The method supports extensible parsing via registered markup extensions\&.

.PP
\fBParameters\fP
.RS 4
\fItext\fP The input text containing markup to be parsed\&. May include YAML front matter or document properties blocks, which will be ignored during parsing\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns\fP
.RS 4
A list of \fBMarkupElement\fP objects representing the parsed elements of the markup text\&. The list will be empty if no elements are found\&.
.RE
.PP

